[normal]example
[normal] our Us Girls project with women under 25 in deprived areas;
[normal]c)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]To create an environment where the norms of women’s experience of sport – 
[normal]i
[normal]e
[normal] that it is less usual, less expected and less catered for than men’s participation – are reversed through our B
[normal]ury project
