[normal]Refurbishing 
[normal]Bury’s
[normal] tennis and netball courts, installing three outdo
[normal]or gyms, modernising the changing rooms in the main leisure centres and starting work to install two mobile swimming pools.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Putting in place an engaged and enthusiastic workforce that understands the barriers to women’s participation and motivation to
[normal] ensure that activities are attractive to attractive, engaging and retentive
[normal]              
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Reaching out to women through social networks and digital platforms to make sure they know the sporting opportunities available to them
